text: Kristian Henrik Rudolf Sjöberg was a athlete and gymnast from Sweden. Kristian competed at the 1896 Summer Olympics. He was born on January 20, 1875 and died on August 1, 1905.Henrik Sjöberg == References == Category:1875 births Category:1905 deaths Category:Olympians for Sweden Category:Swedish athletes Category:Swedish gymnasts Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
